title: Michael Kory Complete Cookbook
description:
With over 190 recipes, the Complete Cookbook includes every recipe from the Breakfast, Lunch & Dinner, and Desserts & Baked Goods Cookbooks. Included as a bonus are the Protein Shakes and Sides & Snacks cookbooks. 

Every recipe is catered to healthy-living and the fitness lifestyle. Included for every recipe is the nutritional information as well as the standard and metric system measurements for each ingredient. The Complete Cookbook has it all.
